title: 62: Dunkin' Donuts in Concord, NH
description:
Grab your plain sticks and your snotty coffee, because we're about to go on quite the journey. First, we read reviews of good old Dunkin' Donuts in the northeast, specifically in Concord, New Hampshire. Then, Alex completes the challenge of finding reviews where people used self defense tools on themselves. And it's just as ridiculous as you think! Tune in to find out where we're going next now that we finished all 50 states!
Go watch our latest YouTube video to see us reveal the man behind the intro: https://youtu.be/l8Qzn-kW2wY
Support us on Patreon at patreon.com/beachtoosandy for a monthly livestream Q&A! 
Buy our merch! https://store.dftba.com/collections/beach-too-sandy-water-too-wet
Logo by Courtney DeKorte. Theme by Mavus White.
Music by PSOVOD and tyops.
